Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.37,0:00:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼晚了有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 有點睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看這樣子 還是沒找到那些護衛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也找了一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.80,0:00:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道團長有發現什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,團長應該不會出事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這種時候居然還能避開要害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大介 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,風槌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我的行動已經被看穿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,吹散 風壁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,玷汙了你副團長的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,先睡會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 都讓副團長幫忙了還這麼慘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是這世界的人類而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼跟個怪物一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,過獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是經驗老道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,與人交戰的經驗老道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼還自豪起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,大介 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他們到死也不會停下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 明明鬧出這麼大動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼沒人過來支援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你就放棄掙扎去死吧 梅爾德團長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我選擇忍辱脫逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,燃燒天地之紅蓮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不論是國王 還是騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,都太掉以輕心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟只是一群人類
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,最後還是得靠我親自出馬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是埃希德大人的旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能說 接下來就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是你的敵人 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,重拳出擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哎喲 不愧是團長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不得不說他辦事真是萬無一失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,差點就被他得逞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來 你的傷怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好像被揍得不輕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這點小傷算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,已經不見了 還說我們掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不過她的介入也在我們的計劃之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟我很有可能受了神之祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到還真有這麼壞心眼的神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不論如何 最大的障礙已經掃除了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,之後只要不被八重檻她們發現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,也就沒什麼問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,國王和宰相現在都跟靈魂出竅了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,教會一直以來也是毫無威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,幹掉團長之後 我們已經無人能擋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 加速吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就像滾下山坡的大石頭一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,朝終點加速吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,朝我理想中的未來加速吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,繆送的貝殼能給我一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,可是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要用來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,別問了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 始大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊是不是遭到襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,對方好像是強盜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有40來個衣衫不整的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,而護衛只有大概15個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,戰力差距這麼大居然還能抗衡 挺厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那個結界品質不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不摧毀結界就無法靠近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,隔著結界遭到魔法攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,強盜們肯定也氣急敗壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 雙方好像都不打算退讓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼大的結界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,至少得是異世界組 不然撐不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可能會花點時間 不過多等等就自己解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,始 幫幫忙 去救救他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,始 謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,發現罪犯馬上踩油門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,駕校不就是這麼教的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒這麼教 你別亂改規定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,既然動手就不能手下留情 殺光他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有慈悲可言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的吧 香織
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那你去吧 沒人敢妨礙你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這臭婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,香織
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,果然 是莉莉對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我就覺得那個結界有點眼熟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,只是沒想到你會出現在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我還有點半信半疑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真是僥倖 看來我的運氣還沒用光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,香織 治療結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是南雲對吧 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,雫她們說過你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你不在的時候香織真是魂不守舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 現在就別提這些了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我還聽說了香織一生難得的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,待會一定要仔細說給我聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,始 她是公主殿下 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,海利希王國的公主 莉莉安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,被人遺忘真是令人痛心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,莉莉 別哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,始他只是有點那什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一般人不可能忘記莉莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你是不是偷偷在罵我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 公主殿下來這種地方幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,愛子老師被抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直覺得 王宮裡的氣氛有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,父皇前所未有地專注於聖教教會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,發瘋似地崇拜埃希德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,信仰無比堅定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,起初 我以為他只是為了籠絡聖教教會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我心裡的違和感始終沒有消散
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不久之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,大家就像生病了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越多的騎士和士兵變得如同行屍走肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,認定南云為異端分子的事情也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他們無視烏爾鎮和奧爾庫斯大迷宮的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,以及愛子老師的異議與反駁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,當然 我向父皇提出了抗議
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可不論我怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他都堅決認定南雲是神的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,父皇看我的眼神也日漸充滿了敵意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,想去找愛子老師談談
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,結果愛子老師被神山的修女抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定修女就是這場異變的幕後黑手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,或者和幕後黑手有關
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我決定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,必須把這件事告訴其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是王宮裡面肯定已經被監視了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以只能找人幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我最先想到的 就是香織和南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,聽雫說過你們往西走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來的事就如你們所見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,為了得到傑根主公的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我拜託隊商的人 帶我一起上路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到 中途居然能見到你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,放在以前 我肯定會覺得這是神的保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我現在非常害怕教會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,總之 得先去救老師才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你別誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是為了你們王國 我只是去救老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,愛子老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她被抓走也有我的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不能放著她不管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果救老師的過程中 異變的元兇出來阻擋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不論對方是誰我都會送他歸西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那就希望一切順利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你了 南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,老師被帶去的神山也是大迷宮之一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這次又能拿到什麼神代魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,始 你真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人又露出那種表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真讓人心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,主人 見了你這副兇惡的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我會濕身的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我的學生們想做的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,掃清異種是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,異種…異種？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我幹嘛 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是南雲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡可是最頂層 而且是在神山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你先冷靜點 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,等我再確認一下有沒有陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有必要這麼驚訝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是已經注意到我來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,儘管我完全隱藏了氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,注意到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是叫了我的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是察覺到我的氣息了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來 你為什麼會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,當然是來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,為了來救我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,特意來救我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不會已經被洗腦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}為了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不行 太突然了 我可是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我只是幫你解開這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,魔力被封印了很不方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,還是說解開之後會出什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你以為是要幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道我被抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,除了我應該沒人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,公主告訴我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,公主？莉莉安娜公主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她親眼目睹了老師被抓走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,之後 她認定王宮裡已經被監視了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不能去告訴天之河他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以獨自逃離了王都
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,尋求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是莉莉安娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你們幫助了她是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,鬧成現在這樣多半也有我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然老師可能不太想看見我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,和其他人會合之前就先忍一忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不想見你是絕對不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,的確 清水同學的事情直到現在我也放不下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,今後 說不定很多事情我都放不下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我也會理解你 當初究竟為何扣動扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,當時沒能認真說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,趁現在讓我好好說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是我害你向同學扣動了扳機 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是按照我的想法行事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,道謝可以 道歉就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不說這些 該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲同學 當心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,教會已經完全認定你為異端分子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 抓走我的人說不定會把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 總之把老師送回去之後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我也還要辦我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,到時候應該也會和教會那些傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你早已下定決心了對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,來得真是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,某種意義上或許正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,魔人族入侵了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛那應該是王都結界被破壞的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,魔人族入侵？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說海利希王國正在遭受入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,完全沒料到這一手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 先和天之河他們會合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,之後再考慮這些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…被分解了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,回答正確
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,異種
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫諾因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,身為神之使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:21:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我要為主人清除棋盤上多餘的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.07,0:23:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 王都入侵
Comment: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-----------------OP-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:03.71,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Tears streaming down your sorrow face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:09.72,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Came a long and painful road, you gave yourself away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:15.05,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You saw everything, heaven to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:21.48,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You say you need a self redemption, to mend the broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:26.90,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Drowning in the dark, no place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:30.65,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}But I am by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:32.49,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You’re not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:38.41,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, shed a light so you won’t disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:44.37,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Cause I know where you belong, save your saddened heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:50.09,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}With a flashback, screaming out but still we’re holding on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:55.51,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Waiting for the break of dawn for a new day to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:58.76,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:04.10,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Stay a little while longer
Comment: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:04.05,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,------------------ED------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全部　期待してみて幻だった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:17.27,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}信じたかった　縋りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身体の底に開いた螺旋状の穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:29.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ボクだけじゃなく　キミにもなんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許されることなど　もう望んじゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:42.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱き寄せてもまた　わからないシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:47.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}躊躇いもなく傷つけた代償か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:52.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}キミの側は　揺れてボクを離れた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:57.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道を違える度に　ボクの後ろに穴が開く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伸びた一本の影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰もが手にし得る　小さな欠片で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:26.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:31.22,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.77,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}期待的一切皆為虛空一場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:17.27,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}破滅的希望　虛偽的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.99,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嵌入身體的傷口深不見底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:29.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不僅是我　你也背負同樣的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早已不再奢望　求得誰人原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:42.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕懷中相擁　徒留輪廓難辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:47.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甘願承傷不曾猶豫的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:52.56,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我步履蹣跚　忍痛離開你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:57.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凜然在上　拋下兩難抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不斷拷問你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幾步對錯　令我身負百孔千瘡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}形單影隻漸行漸遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.62,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望碎片　誰人不曾擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.21,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又能作何掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:26.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凜然在上　拋下兩難抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:31.22,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不斷拷問你我
